Example (Postman / Flutter / React):
GET /api/profile
Authorization: Bearer 1|jdsf98sdf98sdf...

PART 5ï¸âƒ£ â€” TOKEN PERMISSIONS (ADVANCED ðŸ”¥)
Create Token with Ability
$token = $user->createToken('mobile', ['order:create'])->plainTextToken;

Check Ability in Route
Route::get('/orders', function (Request $request) {
    if (!$request->user()->tokenCan('order:create')) {
        abort(403);
    }
});
